data.description: Welcome to this charming home nestled in the picturesque mountainous landscape. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this residence offers a serene retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life. The large great room welcomes you with a cozy fireplace, perfect for relaxing evenings and gatherings with loved ones. The kitchen features matching stainless steel appliances, adding a touch of modern elegance to the rustic charm of the surroundings. Outside, the property offers ample storage space with a 10 X40 shed or extra garage, ideal for housing outdoor equipment and recreational gear. Additionally, there are chicken coops and space for horses, allowing for a self-sustaining lifestyle in harmony with nature. Surrounded by the natural beauty of the mountains, this home provides a tranquil sanctuary where you can unwind and appreciate the breathtaking views. Don't forget to take the virtual tour and schedule your showing today!
